Minyo singing group, <LOCATION>San Jose Taiko</LOCATION> Drum group, <ORGANIZATION>Chidori Band</ORGANIZATION> concert and obon
dancing. The foods include sushi, tempura, teriyaki, barbecued chicken,
skewered teriyaki beef, noodles and strawberry short cake. Because of parking
