   Metropolitan Museum of Art, <LOCATION>Manhattan</LOCATION>: "Jose <LOCATION>Campeche</LOCATION> and His Time: <LOCATION>Puerto Rico</LOCATION>, 1751-1809" -- Almost 50 works by one of <LOCATION>Puerto Rico</LOCATION>'s foremost painters, known for his religious works and detailed portraits of members of Old San Juan society. 
